Characters and Special Forces (Personnel) are some of our most valuable resources.  Characters can engage in missions such as Diplomacy, Sabotage, Recruitment, and Research; characters are also capable of taking on leadership roles including 'Admiral', 'Commander', or 'General'.  Special Forces are small troop units that can each perform a limited number of missions. Special forces available to you include Guerrillas, Infiltrators, Bothan Spies, and Y-wing Longprobes.  These can be used to augment our other personnel as necessary.